text: Maykopsky (masculine), Maykopskaya (feminine), or Maykopskoye (neuter) may refer to: *Maykopsky District, a district of the Republic of Adygea, Russia *Maykopsky (rural locality), a rural locality (a khutor) in Rostov Oblast, Russia *Maykopskoye, a rural locality (a selo) in Krasnodar Krai, Russia
title: Maykopsky
